{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"561","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"每日製造4萬噸廢棄物 菲律賓推垃圾減量","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>最新更新：<span lang='EN-US'>2019/11/04 17:16</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/1108%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 586px;' />&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>菲律賓國家經濟發展局次長艾迪隆（<span lang='EN-US'>Rosemarie Edillon</span>）（左）<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>日表示，<span lang='EN-US'>2016</span>年菲律賓每天製造<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>萬噸廢棄物，平均每天每人製造<span lang='EN-US'>0.4</span>公斤垃圾，可填滿<span lang='EN-US'>106</span>個游泳池。中央社記者陳妍君馬尼拉攝 <span lang='EN-US'>108</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>11</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>日</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>（中央社記者陳妍君馬尼拉<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>日專電）菲律賓國家經濟發展局今天表示，<span lang='EN-US'>2016</span>年菲律賓每天製造<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>萬噸廢棄物，可填滿<span lang='EN-US'>106</span>座游泳池，盼藉由推動「<span lang='EN-US'>5R</span>垃圾減量」等行動促進社會永續發展。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>菲律賓國家經濟發展局（<span lang='EN-US'>NEDA</span>）下午召開記者會。國家經濟發展局副局長艾迪隆（<span lang='EN-US'>Rosemarie Edillon</span>）說，菲律賓人口密度由<span lang='EN-US'>2000</span>年每平方公里<span lang='EN-US'>255</span>人，<span lang='EN-US'>15</span>年間成長到每平方公里<span lang='EN-US'>337</span>人，預估到<span lang='EN-US'>2040</span>年，總人口數將達<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>億<span lang='EN-US'>4000</span>萬人。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>她表示，隨著人口成長，菲律賓都會區空氣品質和水質持續惡化，用水需求增加加劇供水問題，預計氣候變遷將進一步影響淡水供應。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>另外，<span lang='EN-US'>2016</span>年菲律賓每天製造<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>萬噸廢棄物，其中<span lang='EN-US'>56.7%</span>固體廢棄物來源是家庭垃圾；以廢棄物種類來說，<span lang='EN-US'>52.31%</span>是生物可分解垃圾，<span lang='EN-US'>27.78%</span>是可回收垃圾，但未經過適當的回收處理程序。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>艾迪隆說，菲律賓在產品生命週期、替代包裝產品及再生原料回收方面的研究和數據很有限，由於資訊匱乏，消費者傾向選購廉價但不利永續發展的產品。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>她表示，為促進永續消費與生產，菲律賓正整頓長灘島、艾尼島（<span lang='EN-US'>El Nido</span>）、柯倫島（<span lang='EN-US'>Coron</span>）、加勒拉港（<span lang='EN-US'>Puerto Galera</span>）等旅遊勝地環境，並推動「永續用餐習慣計畫」（<span lang='EN-US'>Sustainable Diner project</span>），希望藉由政府、食品業和消費者參與，減少食物浪費。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>艾迪隆說，國家經濟發展局也期盼藉由教育民眾推動「<span lang='EN-US'>5R</span>垃圾減量」，包括拒絕（<span lang='EN-US'>Refuse</span>）一次性塑膠和吸管、減量（<span lang='EN-US'>Reduce</span>）、重複使用（<span lang='EN-US'>Reuse</span>）、回收（<span lang='EN-US'>Recycle</span>）及堆肥（<span lang='EN-US'>Rot</span>），促進零浪費和永續消費與生產的目標。（編輯：周永捷）<span lang='EN-US'>1081104</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/1108%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%932.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 660px;' /></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>菲律賓國家經濟發展局次長艾迪隆（<span lang='EN-US'>Rosemarie Edillon</span>）（前）<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>日表示，<span lang='EN-US'>2016</span>年菲律賓每天製造<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>萬噸廢棄物，盼藉由教育民眾推動<span lang='EN-US'>5R</span>垃圾減量，促進零浪費和永續消費與生產的目標。中央社記者陳妍君馬尼拉攝<span lang='EN-US'> 108</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>11</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>日</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201911040190.aspx</span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-11-08","clk_count":"164"}},"__N_SSG":true}